description: Batman struggles to connect the clues left behind by the Bookbinder. Retracing his steps, he re-examines the evidence, looking for the common thread that will blast the case wide open. Meanwhile, Bruce Wayne and his public misgivings regarding Arkham City are starting to earn him some enemies in City Hall.
name: Welcome to the Slough of Despond, Part 10

description:
Ultra-violent girl gangs fight for power in a strange future where men are zombies. In Vegas, the Black Cherry Bombshells and their leader Regina take control of the bootlegging industry, much to the fury of the local crime boss, a woman called The King.

New girl and quick-thinking trickster Megan joins the Black Cherry gang with a hidden agenda, but soon finds her loyalties conflicted. Meanwhile, a new gang emerges to cause trouble for The King.

At last: A lost Joe Kubert classic sees print! The amazing sci-fi epic THE REDEEMER begins in this issue!

New stories with classic characters ANGEL AND THE APE and the crew of the U.S.S. STEVENS!
name: A Time of Death, A Time of Life

description: Learn the origins of SINESTRA! Once a brilliant anthropologist, she was corrupted by the power of an evil ring. The Green Lanterns may have vanquished her once, but she's back and even more powerful...with a second ring of terrifying power!
name: The Chosen, Part 6

description: Demon hunter Catherine Gregor, her brother Ethan, and the demon Durin are in pursuit of the demon Kanisus, who has stolen the power to return his fallen brethren to Earth and slaughter humanity. An archaic rivalry culminates in a battle between the demon Kanisus and Elias Gregor. When Ethan and Catherine discover their slain father, not only are they faced with his death, but the knowledge that Kanisus has possession of vast quantities of demon blood - which will allow him to raise demons from hell.

An overnight stay turns into a terrifying hell for a young family!

As the horror mounts, the question becomes this: How far would you go to protect your family?

The Vandenreich attacks Soul Society at full strenght, and it's more a massacre than an actual war. The Captains of the Gotei 13 face the Sternritters, and Byakuya takes center stage against the terrifying Äs Nödt, whose Fear-based powers give him a nightmarish edge.

At the same time, Yamamoto goes all-out confronting his ancient enemy Juhabach.

  • Chapter 509: Tenchi Kaijin (天地灰尽 Tenchi Kaijin)
name: Out of Bloom

description: Four teens attempt to film a documentary about The Arrow and end up in way over their heads...
name: [Rec.]

description: Stumbling onto the feud of an old clan of shape-shifters, a college graduate named Joy finds herself looking after a rogue named Rurik. In a cabin in the woods, feelings quickly develop between the two unlikely lovers as Rurik’s people draw close. United in their forbidden love, Joy and Rurik fight a small army of Neurian flesh-eaters who have come to kill Rurik for abandoning their fading clan.
name: GN

Penultimate issue in print.

Cover image is reprinted from the Dandy Annual 1987
Shaky ponders what the encounter with this new group of survivors means for his team and the goals his colony set for him to accomplish.
name: Interlude 9
